en_194321_0	A mentally unstable person has forcefully entered two houses in Galbokka, Urubokka and carried out a knife attack.
en_194321_1	Police said that a 28-year-old woman was killed and a mother aged 64 and her daughter, aged 32 were admitted to Embilipitiya Hospital with critical condition with cut injuries following the attack.
en_194321_2	The incident had occurred at around 7.30 pm yesterday (Jul 01).
en_194321_3	Police said that the 40-year-old suspect committed suicide following the attack.
en_194321_4	Police investigations are underway to ascertain the reason behind the attack.
